data.description: Welcome to your serene 3-bedroom retreat, nestled on a generous corner lot just outside charming Kalkaska. Enveloped by majestic pine trees, this home offers a tranquil escape while still being conveniently close to Traverse City and the region's scenic lakes and trails..................................................  Step inside to discover a newly renovated kitchen featuring stainless appliances. Recent updates also include a durable metal roof, energy-efficient windows, an upgraded electric panel, a new water heater, furnace, and an inviting front porch where you can unwind amidst the natural beauty. ..............................  Additional perks include an attached garage and a spacious shed, providing ample storage space for all your outdoor gear and tools. Don't miss your chance to own this perfect blend of modern comfort and rustic charm, offering the best of both worlds.
